  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Release\u00a011/02/2018 12:00PM CT (17:00 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.15.7-FixedElectronicSignaturesonWindows10\">Fixed Electronic Signatures on Windows 10</h2><p>With the Windows update on October 30, our solution for electronic signatures stopped working\u00a0when using a touch screen in the Edge and Chrome browsers. When attempting to sign with your finger, the page would scroll rather than draw a signature. With this update the issue\u00a0is resolved, and all methods of signing (mouse, touchpad, touchscreen) are working normally.</p>",
